snippet.title: The Fifth Day: Survival Tactics Trailer
snippet.description:
Take a look at the world and some of the features that will be seen in upcoming game, The Fifth Day!

Look for Steam Early Access planned for release on July 25th, 2014!

Steam Page - http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=176587136

Like - https://www.facebook.com/pages/The-Fifth-Day/562668753781257
